flowchart LR
    R[HTTP/RPC 请求] --> G[有界 goroutine]
    G --> A[Admission Control]
    A --> Q[pgxpool 获取队列]

    Q --> C1[Pool Connection 1]
    Q --> C2[Pool Connection 2]
    Q --> C3[Pool Connection N]

    C1 --> B1[PostgreSQL Backend 1]
    C2 --> B2[PostgreSQL Backend 2]
    C3 --> B3[PostgreSQL Backend N]

    B1 --> DB[(shared_buffers / WAL / Locks)]
    B2 --> DB
    B3 --> DB

    Q -.超时.-> E1[Acquire 失败]
    C1 -.网络/Failover.-> E2[旧连接失效]
    B1 -.锁等待.-> E3[连接长期占用]
